description: Drizzled with garlic and lime, this prawn omelette with hints of chilli packs a flavour punch. Serve up this simple meal for breakfast, lunch or dinner.
name: Chilli Prawn Omelette Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 5 ml extra virgin olive oil cooking spray

recipeInstructions.text: Juice 1 lime. Whisk juice, oil and garlic in a jug. Drizzle over omelettes. Sprinkle with sesame seeds. Cut remaining lime into cheeks. Serve with omelettes.
